reviews.text:
To start off, I think, for me at least, the polar blast was too high. It muted almost all of the flavor for me. I've used it before at lower % with no issues. I wanted to mix as is to leave an accurate review. The other flavor combinations here seen great. What I can taste through the coolant is good though. I also tried koolada at 1% and it was much better. I don't know if it was the combo of flavors but all I could taste was sweet cold. I plan on missing without the coolant to try the flavors that way as well. &#xD;
&#xD;
The Fuji does seem to take the top, followed by the first fruits then peach at the end. The flavor is great in that regard.
